name: Dcom
body:
### DCom terminal emulator.

DCom is current in alpha, and runs only on Windows, it has support for ssh, telnet, and serial.


![Screenshot](https://raw.github.com/cdesjardins/DCom/master/img/DComScreen.png)
tagline: A terminal emulator for ssh, telnet, and serial communication.
